I koh mng7 kong2: ¡§Na7 an2-ni goa2 thai3 chheng7 kau3 phoa3-phoa3, chit-ki sip8-ji7-ke3 chiah-nih bai2?¡¨ Thinn-sai3 chiah ka7 i kong2: ¡§Kiann5 thinn-lou7 u7 nng7-khoan2 e5 lang5. Chit-khoan2 si7 hi-seng ka-ki7 e5 mia5-siann, chai5-li7, chi2-u7 ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng, hit-khoan2 e5 lang5, i e5 sann sui2 koh peh8, i gia5 e5 sip8-ji7-ke3 kim kau3 oe7 hoat-kng, li2 khoann3 au7-bin7 teh lai5 hit e5 lang5.....¡¨ Thinn-sai3 po3 i khoann3 chit8 e5 chheng7 peh8-sann, gia5 chit-ki kim e5 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 lang5 tui3 au7-bin7 teh lai5, chiu7 koh kong2: ¡§Iau2 u7 chit8-khoan2 kiann5 thinn-lou7 e5 lang5, sui-jian5 ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 cho3-kang, chong2-si7 toa7-pou7-hun7 si7 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 e5 mia5-siann, chai5-li7 teh tou5-bou5--e5, chiu7-si7 chhin-chhiunn7 li2. Li2 se3-han3 ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 sui-jian5 chin kho2-chhu2, na7-si7 li2 e5 chhut-sek si7 ui7-tioh8 siunn2-phin2, li2 e5 hian3-kim si7 ui7-tioh8 hou7 lang5 o-lo2, li2 thak8 Sin5-hak8-inn7 ia7 si7 chi2-u7 ui7-tioh8 mia5-siann, li2 ti7 kau3-hoe7 chi2-u7 tui-kiu5 ka-ki7 e5 te7-ui7 kap beng5-u7, sou2-i2 li2 e5 sip8-ji7-ke3 senn-sian, li2 e5 sann phoa3-phoa3.¡¨
