1. I u7 khi2 seng3-tian7, Sou2-lo5-bun5 iau2-boe7 khi2 seng3-tian7 e5 i2-cheng5, Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 iok-kui7 si7 khng3 ti7 hoe7-bou7 nih. Hoe7-bou7 chiu7-si7 pou3-pinn5 e5 i3-su3. Lan2 chai hoe7-bou7 m7-si7 chin ho2 e5 chhu3, si7 lim5-si5 eng7 pou3 lai5 tah--e5. Si7 cha2-si5 I2-sek-liat8 peh-sinn3 chhut Ai-kip8, ti7 khong3-ia2 phiau-liu5, lai5-lai5 khi3-khi3 toe3 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 soa2-lai5 soa2-khi3 e5 pou3-pinn5. Tann I2-sek-liat8 lang5 i2-keng kian3-kok lah. Pun2 i e5 lau7-pe7 Tai7-pit8 chiu7 pi7-pan7 beh khi2. Na7-si7 Siong7-te3 m7 ai3 Tai7-pit8 khi2, I ai3 Sou2-lo5-bun5 khi2. Sou2-lo5-bun5 chiu7 chiau3 Siong7-te3 sou2 chi2-si7 i e5 lau7-pe7 Tai7-pit8 e5 hong-hoat lai5 khi2. Chhai5-liau7 long2 eng7 chin ho2 e5 bok8-chhai5, ho2 chioh8, kim, gun5, tang5, hek8-chia2 si7 tiu5, si, po2-chioh8. Khi2 liau2 hui-siong5 sui2. Chu7 kou2-cha2 kau3 hian7-kim, boe7-bat u7 hiah sui2 e5 tian7.
2. Ngia5-chih Iok-kui7, lai5 an-ti3 ti7 seng3-tian7 e5 chi3-seng3-sou2, seng3-tian7 u7 hun chi3-seng3-sou2 kap seng3-sou2, ia7 u7 hun lai7-inn7 kap goa7-inn7. Seng3-sou2 u7 khng3 ki2-toh pai5-piann2 kap teng-tai5 thang tiam2-teng, tiong-ng u7 khng3 hiunn-toann5 thang sio-hiunn. Hiah e5 long2 si7 eng7 siang7 ho2 e5 kim lai5 choe3--e5. Seng3-sou2 kap chi3-seng3-sou2 e5 tiong-kan u7 chiong tiu5-si khi3 chit u7 thinn-sai3 e5 pou3-li5 chah8-teh. Lai7-bin7 kio3-choe3 chi3-seng3-sou2. Chi3-seng3-sou2 chi2-u7 khng3 Iok-kui7 ti7 hia. Iok-kui7 chiu7-si7 piau2-si7 ¡§Siong7-te3 kap lang5 sann-kap ti7-teh¡¨. Iok-kui7 si7 eng7 kim choe3--e5, kui7-teng2 u7 nng7-sian thinn-sai3 thian2-khui sit8, sio-ng3 kiong2-chhiu2, kui7-loh8 teh ki5-to2 e5 siong7. Hit-ui7 kio3 choe3 ¡§Si-un-sou2¡¨ chiu7-si7 mui2-ni5 che3-si-thau5 eng7 iunn5-ko e5 huih hiu3 ti7 hia, lai5 the3 peh-sinn3 siok8-choe7, koh kiu5 in. Kui7-lai7 u7 khng3 Ma2-na2, kap chap8-tiau5-kai3 e5 chioh8-pi.
